---
title: Herby Beef Meatballs & Cauliflower Mash with Steamed Broccoli & Balsamic Green Salad
description: Get ready to fall head over heels for this rich, hearty dish that’s a splendid symphony of flavours. The secret is combining the
meatballs with the garlic and herb seasoning, tomato sugo and garlic. With a bed of fluffy cauliflower mash to finish it off, you better be ready to savour every taste — it’ll be gone before you know it!

